<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="systems-implementation-the-search-bottleneck">Systems Implementation: The Search Bottleneck</h2>
<p>While the math is elegant, the cs challenge is the <strong>State Space Explosion</strong>. For a game like Chess, the tree is too large to solve. We must implement a depth-limited search with an evaluation function.</p>
