<section id="conclusion" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
<p>The gap between the <strong>Minimax Theorem</strong> and a <strong>Stockfish implementation</strong> is where the most interesting work happens. One is about existence proofs; the other is about cache locality, bitboards, and pruning branches of the state space.</p>


</section>

